{"tid":772817,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"市民拾獲價值42萬元勞力士報案 警員涉企圖據為己有被控","createTime":"2018-08-09T05:12:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-12T13:39:01.000Z","uid":39464,"like":38,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"a43f19097e80e28d9ba44b11f9239315b6d09013","tid":772817,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T05:12:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180809/large/1533790505_6a82.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180809%2Flarge%2F1533790505_6a82.jpg&h=6661c6ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n市民路不拾遺，於去年6月拾獲價值42.5萬元的「勞力士」（Cally-Daytona）名錶後，將錶交到長沙灣警署。惟報案室警員涉監守自盜，一度將名錶據為己有，重案組接手展開調查及咨詢律政司後，將警員拘捕並控以盗竊罪。案件今天於西九龍裁判法院提堂，辯方申請押後答辯，以便索取法律意見。<br />\n<br />\n被告警員周合駿(27歲)，被控於去年6月26日於長沙灣警署1樓報案室內，偷竊一隻銀色錶帶、棕色外圈及淺藍色錶面的「勞力士」手錶。裁判官將案押後至8月30日再訊，被告獲准以1萬元保釋。<br />\n<br />\n【案件編號：WKCC3526/18】<br />\n<br />\n記者羅日昇<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180809/58541560\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180809%2F58541560&d=YAiwTaAOMRcLGJI5bW5Urhxs2jlPaATBKfveiEY0UFo%3D&h=86fe7772\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180809%2F58541560&h=2c1de806\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180809/58541560</a>"},{"pid":"179656796b4e5d013c068ffd5ea1cf746450a79a","tid":772817,"uid":46042,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T05:13:23.000Z","msg":"究竟呢單野係點<br />\n<br />\n之前又話隻錶係假<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd698b6416aa529283d8899e6369ecb56085de0f","tid":772817,"uid":41317,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T05:13:30.000Z","msg":"今次喱個係當值警員"},{"pid":"292753d48798006b6a5bc674be9b84319771aaf5","tid":772817,"uid":5267,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T05:16:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"207d2efc5cdaf15b3ba207886bb90c5eb9cc03f0","tid":772817,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T05:16:14.000Z","msg":"男警涉去年在報案室偷竊一隻價值42.5萬元的「勞力士」手表，該手表為一名市民尋獲交還到警署的失物。男警今在西九龍裁判法院被控一項盜竊罪，暫時毋須答辯，獲准保釋，案件將轉至區域法院處理，押後至8月30日再提訊。<br />\n<br />\n被告周合駿（27歲）報稱住深井一私人屋苑，今透過私人律師稱他10月會到外地旅行，希望保釋期間能離境，惟裁判官稱下次提訊時再處理。<br />\n<br />\n控罪指，被告去年6月26日在長沙灣警署1樓報案室內，偷竊一隻屬於男子鍾曉峰的銀色表帶、棕色外圈、淺藍色表面的「勞力士」手表，型號為Cally-Daytona 116506，價值42.5萬元。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，事主在球場遺失了手表並報失，其後事主的隊友在髒衣服中尋獲該手表，遂交還到警署，惟負責處理此事的警員疑將手表放進自己的腰包。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180809/s00001/1533787205408\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180809%2Fs00001%2F1533787205408&d=YAiwTaAOMRcLGJI5bW5Urhxs2jlPaATBKfveiEY0UFo%3D&h=39d68bce\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180809%2Fs00001%2F1533787205408&h=642a10a6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180809/s00001/1533787205408</a>"},{"pid":"b23bd67408a6bfd7bce581e5d9ebb76321a271a8","tid":772817,"uid":29093,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T05:16:53.000Z","msg":"以為又係追擊post"},{"pid":"e7126f98ecd250c93092d42c2edf1a5680412cd1","tid":772817,"uid":511,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"dd698b6416aa529283d8899e6369ecb56085de0f","tid":772817,"uid":41317,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T05:13:30.000Z","msg":"今次喱個係當值警員"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T05:17:10.000Z","msg":"當更警+1分<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c70999f6de972460bc9b74ff5d31f88a6c23e960","tid":772817,"uid":26752,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T05:17:46.0